{"id":305967,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/维权网-中央巡视组进驻安徽宿州市，访民被严控/","date":"2013-07-28T06:49:07Z","modified":"2013-07-28T06:49:07Z","title":"维权网 | 中央巡视组进驻安徽宿州市，访民被严控打压","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员周维林报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日</span><span>中央巡视组进驻安徽省宿州市南苑宾馆，一些访民到宾馆反映上访诉求，当地政府出动众多警察和政府官员阻拦访民，警察抓了一些访民；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日上午</span><span>，</span><span>访民再次到南苑宾馆找中央巡视组反映诉求，依旧被警察和官员阻拦，警察再次抓人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据访民反映，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日</span><span>宿州女访民邵大芬为此被警方以涉嫌敲诈政府的罪名刑事拘留，闫淑华被行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张文英、徐思兰于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日被警察抓到派出所关押两天后又被送回家，由警察严密监控，后由街道办事处、社居委的维稳人员带到宾馆非法拘禁。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>宿州市的王风云在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日被警察及政府官员抓住塞进警车后逃脱，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日上午</span><span>到南苑宾馆时被其所在乡政府官员警告：你的手机被监控了，定性你串访，得治你等等。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据王风云称</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日上午</span><span>政府官员打她手机，叫她到乡政府去，有事要问她。王风云因恐惧政府以“串访”为由对她进行打击报复没有去。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}